1. What’s one of the key benefits of bringing external data into Sales Cloud?
Ans: B. It allows for more detailed insights and improved decision-making.

2. You’re using customer segmentation data in Sales Cloud to understand your customers better. Based on their buying behavior and engagement levels, what’s an effective strategy to enhance your marketing efforts?
Ans: B. Identify high-potential customers and tailor targeted campaigns to meet their specific needs and preferences.
